snippet.title: I'm looking for 3024 people | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The dead computer engineer had only one purpose, to reveal the true face of the company he worked for. Now, this mission is up to a hacker and 3024 people.

"I'm looking for 3024 people" is an alternate reality game developed by Bakodun Game Studios. In this adventure; you will have to infiltrate the company and examine the leaked documents.

Watch Frank's Message: https://youtu.be/BQHcOdXuNBI

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1946010/Im_looking_for_3024_people
Epic Store: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/im-looking-for-3024-people-1cdae4
Microsoft Store: https://www.microsoft.com/store/productId/9N0242QPVNC2

You can find all the details about the mission on this website: https://www.frankscomputer.online/
Discord: https://discord.gg/Uq9xfrNEwK

Bakodun Game Studios: https://www.bakodungamestudios.com
